title: NFL Week 5 Preview and Quarter-Season Review
itunes:title: NFL Week 5 Preview and Quarter-Season Review
description:
Cynthia and Money go through the analytics and tell you which NFL teams have performed differently than expected through the first 4 weeks of the 2017 season before previewing the matchup of the week (Packers vs. Cowboys), tackling the Frelund Four-cast, and giving you insight into each NFL game this weekend.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
